text: This is one of the most affordable yet professional printing shops I’ve come across. The lady boss is friendly and easy to work with, making the experience even better. Highly recommend giving this shop a try!
Aunt very friendly and price is very cheap compared to many places , paid only 1 dollar for two sided A4 colour, print quality top notched and the aunt knows her stuff well . Must visit

Great service and affordable as well! The auntie was very nice and accommodating.  Printed about 60 pages and was only charged about $15 ( mix of both plain and coloured pages). She even went through the file again to make sure correct printing process. Binding was really nice too! Auntie was also super friendly and funny! They offer their services via whatsapp as well ! Will come again for more printing matters.

I live at Sembawang but my friend recommended me to print my poster and assignment artefacts here and it was definitely worth the trip down. The aunty was super helpful and tried her best to cater to the printing specifics (which was v troublesome) I wanted. I’m very thankful for this quick and smooth transaction and would definitely come back again if I needed a printing job done! Thank you aunty!!! :-)
the lady was very helpful and insightful to my request of laminating an odd size worksheet (super a3 to a2). would definitely come back again for her!
